<DOCNO>WT25-B17-3</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA026-000271-B009-226</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.knooppunt.be:80/fr/info/man/agent/csfaqpst.htm 194.10.201.200 19970108203344 text/html 5738
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
MIME-Version: 1.0
