<DOCNO>WT25-B17-8</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA087-000628-B039-94</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.knooppunt.be:80/ned/info/man/agent/csfaqcfg.htm 194.10.201.200 19970122070219 text/html 13158
