Press ? for Help, q to Quit, u to go up a menu Page: 2/5

Receiving Directory...
		Connecting...
Retrieving Directory..\

Internet Gopher Information Client 2.0 pl11 Economic Democracy Information 
Network (EDIN)
 -->  1.  About the EDIN Gopher/
2.  The Economy (General Resources)/
3.  Economic Conversion and Peace Resources/
4.  Labor Issues/
5.  Race and Racism/
6.  Gender and Sexuality/
7.  Environment (from IGC)/
